A warm, intimate Studio Ghibli-style illustration of a young family gathered in a cozy Singapore apartment on a tropical Christmas evening. Soft golden lamplight illuminates the scene as parents sit with small twin children near a modest decorated tree with simple ornaments. Through large windows, the distinctive Singapore skyline glows at dusk with humid tropical clouds. A ceiling fan spins lazily overhead. The color palette blends warm ambers and soft greens, with delicate hand-painted textures on fabric and foliage. Palm fronds frame the window edges, blending festive winter traditions with equatorial warmth. The mood is peaceful, personal, and quietly joyful—a small moment of family connection amid a bustling city.
